reviewText: This is a great product.  It gives you an escape for all the mind boggling troubles & problems in the world.
Wow, Outstanding photography, well worth the time to watch.
Can't be used n SONY DVD players....perhaps others. Since produced in UK there are restrictions- nothing about this in the Amazon description to advise buyer. I may have to return.
I have enjoyed the spectacular underwater shots of ocean wildlife.  Good quality dvd.
I always love Attenborough's narration on these nature DVDs.  I was not disappointed with this one.
Each disc was blank.  I sent it back and was reimbursed
Not one of the discs in this package would play on my BlueRay/DVD player.  Every other DVD in my collection plays fine.  I would like to return this for a full refund.
I think it's a great series - but it WILL NOT PLAY in US machines.  Wish that had been made clear in big letters up front.
Thank you I enjoy this selection.
